productDescription:
How cute is this small version of The Woven Bag. Inspired by the gorgeous designs of Woven Palm. Discover this luxurious bag, handcrafted in Amsterdam.

This handbag is made of high quality leather. Perfect for everyday use or when you like to get into the beachy vibes. The perfect thickness enables the bag to keep its shape and be light weighted at the same time.
